'''Ceramic mixing technology''' is used to mix and blend [[ceramic materials|ceramics]] to create end products such as: ceramic powder blends, [[injection molding]] feedstock, electronics, decorative finishes, [[refractory]] linings, batteries and [[fuel cell]]s, [[Thermal conductivity|thermally conductive pastes]], investment casting slurries, [[dental ceramics]] and advanced composites.

A wide range of equipment is available for these requirements.

